    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends üëã, Welcome To aGuideHub! ‚ù§Ô∏è In this tutorial, we will learn how to give space between two columns in bootstrap. To give space between two-column‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Hi Friends üëã,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aGuideHub! ‚ù§Ô∏è</p>\n<p>In this tutorial, we will learn how to give space between two columns in bootstrap.</p>\n<p>To give space between two-column, put <code class=\"language-text\">col-md-offset-2</code> class to create space in two columns.</p>\n<p>We can keep space between columns by using normal CSS but here we will use the Bootstrap framework for that. In this article, we will keep a measured gap between columns by the following methods.</p>\n<p><strong><em>Method using columns offset:</em></strong> The offset class is used to increase the left margin of a column. The class <code class=\"language-text\">col-md-offset-2</code> moves <code class=\"language-text\">col-md-3</code> by 3 columns.</p>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Includes bootstrap view</li>\n<li>Includes bootstrap library</li>\n<li>Define its class name</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Step 1: Includes bootstrap view</h3>\n<p>To ensure proper rendering and touch zooming for all devices, add the responsive viewport meta tag to your <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;head></code>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>viewport<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">content</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 1: Includes bootstrap library</h3>\n<p>First of all, load the Bootstrap framework CSS into the head tag of your webpage.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Bootstrap CSS --></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>link</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">rel</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token attr-name\">integrity</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">crossorigin</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>anonymous<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 2: Define its class name</h3>\n<p>The offset class is used to increase the left margin of a column. The class <code class=\"language-text\">col-md-offset-2</code> moves <code class=\"language-text\">col-md-3</code> by 3 columns.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\">    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>container<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text-center<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Space between two columns in bootstrap<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>row<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>col-md-5 bg-warning a<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>aGuideHub<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token 